description: Elderly people and others with difficulty using computers and tablets may prefer a voice interface to review email messages.  This skill is designed to be similar to voice mail, but it can print.  Full instructions are available online at http://email-skill.blogspot.com
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask my email to find messages from the last two weeks
Alexa Ask my email to find all my starred messages
name: my email
shortDescription: Read, manage and print your GMail using your voice
